[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="EnemyStats" format=3]

; The Gnat: the first flyer. Hovers at a perch beside and above you — where
; tier-camping used to be safe — then commits to a full-2D dive you can roll
; under or parry. Paper health on purpose: one poke kills it, so the threat is
; attention pressure, not a health bar. Something the digging woke.

